Hey Friends!! I would really appreciate it if you could help my small business out in an easy way! It only takes a few seconds & would seriously help my business! 
Facebook has a new feature & it takes seconds to do!

I’d really appreciate it if you could go to thetwistedgypsy https://www.facebook.com/thetwistedgypsy.net/

Scroll across the top, go to ‘COMMUNITY’
Click 'INVITE FRIENDS'
Click ‘ALL'
Wait 10-15 seconds for the invitations to send - it’s as simple as that -

Supporting small businesses doesn’t require spending money. It’s as simple as sharing, liking and promoting! 🎄 Merry Christmas to you all! I honestly wouldn’t be where I am today in my business without all of your love and support! Love & appreciate you all! **Copy and pasted from another small business, but it’s so helpful!**
